commit_message:
Split snapshot method in libvirt driver

Separate 4 methods from snapshot call in the driver:
* preparing;
* making snapshot;
* uploading to the glance;
* cleanup;

Add calls for that 4 methods in nova compute. Move snapshot
functionality from nova compute to nova conductor (just API calls
to nova compute, without error handling yet);

Change-Id: I805a87c83766d894d015b03c4abaa0fd170b9b5d
Blueprint: glance-snapshot-tasks

