commit_message:
Reduce and re-use hardcoded string values

Reason:
 - A lot of duplicated hardcoded strings responsible for instance statuses;
 - For better refactoring all duplicates should be defined in one place and
   re-used wherever they are needed.
Changes:
 - Statuses refactoring;
 - were terminated duplicated hardcoded string;
 - updated status determining flow;
 - attr renaming.

Change-Id: I6514a0848dc630e110fa8629441dfeabbf1695c7
Closes-Bug: #1267853
